com.intel.fightclub.cloud.download

Class GcmLtoDownloadService

  • java.lang.Object
    • android.content.Context
      • android.content.ContextWrapper
        • android.app.Service
          • com.google.android.gms.gcm.GcmTaskService
            • com.intel.fightclub.cloud.download.GcmLtoDownloadService
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    android.content.ComponentCallbacks, android.content.ComponentCallbacks2

    @ThreadSafe
public final class GcmLtoDownloadService
extends com.google.android.gms.gcm.GcmTaskService
    This service downloads LTO file. It expected that LTO file is quite small and can be downloaded in 3 minutes limit. So we don't use proxy pattern used in UploadScheduler. Note 1: Don't forget to add &lt;uses-permission android:name="android.permission.RECEIVE_BOOT_COMPLETED" /&gt; into AndroidManifest.xml an GcmNetworkManager requires it! Note 2: Service deletes old file before downloading if they exists. Beware if using this service for downloading other then LTO files. Useful command to dump, whether task was scheduled: adb shell dumpsys activity service GcmService --endpoints GcmLtoDownloadService
